    <div class="body">
        <p>The length of a given content should also be proovable.</p>

<p>testEmpty - for testing if a string (or value) is empty
testLength - for testing the length of a given string
 - min = minimum  length
 - max = maximum length (optional);</p>

<p><code>
testLength($key, $min, $max = null)
{
    $length =strlen($key);
    if ($length &gt; $min){
        return true;
    } else if (($max !== null) and ($length &lt; $max)) {
        return true;
    }
    return false;
}
</code></p>

